{"tid":966351,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"資產財富管理業職業博覽2019","createTime":"2019-01-02T17:26:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T17:39:11.000Z","uid":40384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e0d2c6c7aa6e550c8c51e1e51bbe022743359a48","tid":966351,"uid":40384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T17:26:17.000Z","msg":"「資產財富管理業職業博覽2019」為期半天，主題是「跨躍 &bull; 創未來」，是學生與資產財富管理業 機構和資深從業員進行溝通以及互動的機會。通過不同的主題分享，探索資產財富管理業的最新趨勢及發展機遇，獲取 「資產財富管理業暑期實習計劃2019」的第一手資訊，並可就個人履歷表免費得到專業意見**。<br />\n<br />\n詳情如下：<br />\n日期：2019年1月12日 (星期六)<br />\n時間：下午2:00 - 下午5:00（下午1:30開始登記）<br />\n地點：教育局九龍塘教育服務中心（九龍塘地鐵站E出口）<br />\n*所有分享環節將以廣東話進行<br />\n**有興趣學生可攜同履歷表作查詢。(名額有限)<br />\n歡迎八大資助院校學生參與！<br />\n活動詳情及報名﹕<a href=\"https://www.wamtalent.org.hk/eng/promotion_&amp;_education/career_fairs.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wamtalent.org.hk%2Feng%2Fpromotion_%26_education%2Fcareer_fairs.html&d=avmIg8rHyY0amRrLLBcajf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=3bd3b6d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wamtalent.org.hk/eng/promotion_&amp;_education/career_fairs.html</a><br />\n<br />\n主辦單位：香港特別行政區政府財經事務及庫務局<br />\n執行伙伴：香港證券及投資學會<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uq6wkwG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUq6wkwG.jpg&h=23e4fad2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef6931a6eb091d8d4db67de85e42fe8e008dfadb","tid":966351,"uid":17379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T17:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}